01:00:54,179 --> 01:00:54,900
[SPEAKER_00] Ali

1586
01:00:54,900 --> 01:00:57,400
[SPEAKER_00] pritom ne smije zaboraviti

1587
01:00:57,400 --> 01:00:58,440
[SPEAKER_00] kako nije na njoj

1588
01:00:58,440 --> 01:00:59,760
[SPEAKER_00] uvjeriti ga u tu istinu.

1589
01:00:59,820 --> 01:01:02,260
[SPEAKER_00] U vanđelju po Ivanu u šestom pogledu

1590
01:01:02,260 --> 01:01:02,699
[SPEAKER_00] čitamo

1591
01:01:02,699 --> 01:01:04,159
[SPEAKER_00] Nitko ne može doći k meni

1592
01:01:04,159 --> 01:01:05,599
[SPEAKER_00] ako ga ne povuče otac

1593
01:01:05,599 --> 01:01:06,440
[SPEAKER_00] koji me posla.

1594
01:01:06,440 --> 01:01:07,659
[SPEAKER_00] Znači

1595
01:01:07,659 --> 01:01:09,960
[SPEAKER_00] ako žena svoje mužu

1596
01:01:09,960 --> 01:01:11,420
[SPEAKER_00] ne prestano kvoca

1597
01:01:11,420 --> 01:01:13,119
[SPEAKER_00] stalno prigovara

1598
01:01:13,119 --> 01:01:15,719
[SPEAKER_00] i sili ga da prihvati istinu.

1599
01:01:15,719 --> 01:01:17,280
[SPEAKER_00] znači možeš biti u pravu

1600
01:01:17,280 --> 01:01:18,380
[SPEAKER_00] kako god hoćeš

1601
01:01:18,380 --> 01:01:20,239
[SPEAKER_00] ali to nije način

1602
01:01:20,239 --> 01:01:21,300
[SPEAKER_00] na koji to treba raditi

1603
01:01:21,300 --> 01:01:23,500
[SPEAKER_00] i tad si prestupila uputak

1604
01:01:23,500 --> 01:01:25,099
[SPEAKER_00] iz prve Petrove poslanice

1605
01:01:25,099 --> 01:01:25,699
[SPEAKER_00] koja kaže

1606
01:01:25,699 --> 01:01:27,300
[SPEAKER_00] tako i vi žene

1607
01:01:27,300 --> 01:01:29,039
[SPEAKER_00] pokoravajte sa svojim muževima

1608
01:01:29,039 --> 01:01:30,579
[SPEAKER_00] ako su neki od njih možda

1609
01:01:30,579 --> 01:01:31,760
[SPEAKER_00] neposlušni riječi

1610
01:01:31,760 --> 01:01:33,760
[SPEAKER_00] da i bez riječi budu pridobiveni

1611
01:01:33,760 --> 01:01:34,860
[SPEAKER_00] življenjem vas žena

1612
01:01:34,860 --> 01:01:36,400
[SPEAKER_00] pošto promotre vaše

1613
01:01:36,400 --> 01:01:38,340
[SPEAKER_00] bogoljubno i čisto življenje.

1614
01:01:39,980 --> 01:01:41,519
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim, ako istinu kažemo

1615
01:01:41,519 --> 01:01:42,480
[SPEAKER_00] zaista obazrivo

1616
01:01:42,480 --> 01:01:44,219
[SPEAKER_00] u ljubavi primjerenog tona

1617
01:01:44,219 --> 01:01:46,119
[SPEAKER_00] koji ne umanjuje

1618
01:01:46,119 --> 01:01:46,980
[SPEAKER_00] naše poštovanje

1619
01:01:46,980 --> 01:01:47,780
[SPEAKER_00] prema njemu

1620
01:01:47,780 --> 01:01:49,500
[SPEAKER_00] tek tada je to ispravno.

1621
01:01:49,500 --> 01:01:52,760
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam ovako malo živac

1622
01:01:52,760 --> 01:01:55,980
[SPEAKER_00] i muž mi često zna reć

1623
01:01:55,980 --> 01:01:58,119
[SPEAKER_00] možeš reći najveću istinu

1624
01:01:58,119 --> 01:02:00,639
[SPEAKER_00] ali ako kažeš krivim tonom

1625
01:02:00,639 --> 01:02:02,260
[SPEAKER_00] ja ne daj ne mogu

1626
01:02:02,260 --> 01:02:03,360
[SPEAKER_00] ja ne daj ne želim

1627
01:02:03,360 --> 01:02:04,820
[SPEAKER_00] nego jednostavno ne mogu prihvatiti.

1628
01:02:04,820 --> 01:02:06,119
[SPEAKER_00] I to je to.

1629
01:02:06,119 --> 01:02:07,639
[SPEAKER_00] Mi u konačnici

1630
01:02:07,639 --> 01:02:08,800
[SPEAKER_00] prvenstveno svoga muža

1631
01:02:08,800 --> 01:02:09,320
[SPEAKER_00] i svoju ženu

1632
01:02:09,320 --> 01:02:10,099
[SPEAKER_00] trebamo poštivati

1633
01:02:10,099 --> 01:02:11,559
[SPEAKER_00] kao ljubljeno djete Bože.

1634
01:02:11,559 --> 01:02:12,619
[SPEAKER_00] Znači kao što bi poštivao

1635
01:02:12,619 --> 01:02:13,780
[SPEAKER_00] nekog na ulici

1636
01:02:13,780 --> 01:02:15,619
[SPEAKER_00] samo zato što je to

1637
01:02:15,619 --> 01:02:16,860
[SPEAKER_00] čovjek

1638
01:02:16,860 --> 01:02:18,579
[SPEAKER_00] Božje stvorenje

1639
01:02:18,579 --> 01:02:20,340
[SPEAKER_00] jednako tako traži svoga muža

1640
01:02:20,340 --> 01:02:21,320
[SPEAKER_00] pa možda i više.

1641
01:02:21,320 --> 01:02:25,019
[SPEAKER_00] Jer ispoštovanje prema mužu

1642
01:02:25,019 --> 01:02:26,179
[SPEAKER_00] toliko toga proizlazi

1643
01:02:26,179 --> 01:02:27,920
[SPEAKER_00] pa čak i spolnost.

1644
01:02:27,920 --> 01:02:29,699
[SPEAKER_00] Ja se sad ne bi previše tu

1645
01:02:29,699 --> 01:02:32,659
[SPEAKER_00] tu možda

1646
01:02:32,659 --> 01:02:37,019
[SPEAKER_00] dotaknula spolnosti

1647
01:02:37,019 --> 01:02:38,440
[SPEAKER_00] ali bih voljela povezati

1648
01:02:38,659 --> 01:02:41,219
[SPEAKER_00] poštovanje koji velike utječe na našu spolnost u braku.

1649
01:02:41,219 --> 01:02:43,360
[SPEAKER_00] Naš brak možemo promatrati kao jedan tronožac

1650
01:02:43,360 --> 01:02:47,400
[SPEAKER_00] koji se temelji na našoj zajedničkoj molitvi,

1651
01:02:47,400 --> 01:02:49,679
[SPEAKER_00] na našoj komunikaciji i na spolnosti.

1652
01:02:49,679 --> 01:02:53,920
[SPEAKER_00] Može nešto štekat jedno vrijeme od toga

1653
01:02:53,920 --> 01:02:55,960
[SPEAKER_00] i možda taj tronožac još i držati,

1654
01:02:55,960 --> 01:02:58,619
[SPEAKER_00] ali kad ta će pokleknuti pod pritiskom.

1655
01:02:58,619 --> 01:03:03,360
[SPEAKER_00] Nažalost imamo brašnih parova

1656
01:03:03,360 --> 01:03:04,940
[SPEAKER_00] koji nama dolaze na molitve

1657
01:03:04,940 --> 01:03:06,559
[SPEAKER_00] gdje ono žena otvoreno kaže da

1658
01:03:06,559 --> 01:03:09,480
[SPEAKER_00] onaj muž već deset godina nisu imali odnos.

1659
01:03:11,480 --> 01:03:12,699
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim, kakav je to brak?

1660
01:03:12,699 --> 01:03:13,639
[SPEAKER_00] Šta je to?

1661
01:03:13,639 --> 01:03:18,099
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto?

1662
01:03:18,099 --> 01:03:22,659
[SPEAKER_00] Jesmo zakazali tu ulogama i žene i muškarca?

1663
01:03:22,659 --> 01:03:23,579
[SPEAKER_00] Sigurno jesmo.

1664
01:03:28,039 --> 01:03:32,119
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, ako muž uživa naše poštovanje,

1665
01:03:32,119 --> 01:03:34,099
[SPEAKER_00] uvijek ćemo mu biti privlačne.

1666
01:03:34,099 --> 01:03:35,840
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam u to sigurna.

1667
01:03:35,840 --> 01:03:39,159
[SPEAKER_00] Uvijek ćemo biti privlačne

1668
01:03:39,159 --> 01:03:41,579
[SPEAKER_00] ako on uvažava i ima naše poštovanje.

1669
01:03:41,579 --> 01:03:45,900
[SPEAKER_00] Naš stav utječe na našu spolnost.

1670
01:03:45,900 --> 01:03:49,559
[SPEAKER_00] Muževi trebaju osjeti da su poštovani

1671
01:03:49,559 --> 01:03:51,079
[SPEAKER_00] i poželjni od svojih žena,

1672
01:03:51,079 --> 01:03:53,599
[SPEAKER_00] jer kad se gubi to, gubi se privlačnost,

1673
01:03:53,599 --> 01:03:55,119
[SPEAKER_00] a mi žene gubimo interes.

1674
01:03:58,039 --> 01:04:00,820
[SPEAKER_00] gubimo interes za svoga muža u tom pogledu.

1675
01:04:00,820 --> 01:04:06,880
[SPEAKER_00] Voljela bi se ovdje osvonuti malo

1676
01:04:06,880 --> 01:04:09,820
[SPEAKER_00] na one žene čiji su muževi loši

1677
01:04:09,820 --> 01:04:16,599
[SPEAKER_00] i zaista nama dolaze žene koje imaju

1678
01:04:16,599 --> 01:04:20,719
[SPEAKER_00] zaista muževe koji im gaze dostojanstvo

1679
01:04:20,719 --> 01:04:25,960
[SPEAKER_00] i vjerujem da Bog nije zamislio takve brakove

1680
01:04:25,960 --> 01:04:27,280
[SPEAKER_00] za njih ni takve živote.

1681
01:04:28,039 --> 01:04:33,440
[SPEAKER_00] Ali zaista vas pozivam da ga i dalje poštojete.

1682
01:04:33,440 --> 01:04:36,880
[SPEAKER_00] Znači morate zadržati poštovanje prema njemu.

1683
01:04:36,880 --> 01:04:38,539
[SPEAKER_00] Koliko god to je teško bilo.

1684
01:04:38,539 --> 01:04:40,880
[SPEAKER_00] Mi u svakom odnosu u životu trebamo gledati

1685
01:04:40,880 --> 01:04:42,119
[SPEAKER_00] koja je naša odgovornost.

1686
01:04:42,119 --> 01:04:46,239
[SPEAKER_00] Naša odgovornost je poštovat ga.

1687
01:04:46,239 --> 01:04:48,659
[SPEAKER_00] Mi često kažemo je bilo lako blaženoj

1688
01:04:48,659 --> 01:04:50,440
[SPEAKER_00] djevice Marija, ona imala svetog Josipa.

1689
01:04:50,440 --> 01:04:56,639
[SPEAKER_00] Netko mora početi u tom krugu ljubavi, poštovanja.

1690
01:04:56,639 --> 01:04:58,400
[SPEAKER_00] Netko treba napraviti prvi korak.

1691
01:04:58,400 --> 01:05:03,059
[SPEAKER_00] Ja zaista vjerujem da je uloga žene ogromna

1692
01:05:03,059 --> 01:05:06,460
[SPEAKER_00] i nezamjenjiva u životu crkve,

1693
01:05:06,460 --> 01:05:08,719
[SPEAKER_00] u životu zajednice, u životu obitelji,

1694
01:05:08,719 --> 01:05:09,559
[SPEAKER_00] i društvo općenito.

1695
01:05:09,559 --> 01:05:12,300
[SPEAKER_00] I zaista vjerujem da ljubav

1696
01:05:12,300 --> 01:05:14,059
[SPEAKER_00] može sve promijeniti.

1697
01:05:14,059 --> 01:05:16,760
[SPEAKER_00] Postoji svjedočanstvo jednog

1698
01:05:16,760 --> 01:05:19,519
[SPEAKER_00] svećenika koji je bio

1699
01:05:19,519 --> 01:05:21,340
[SPEAKER_00] ovisnik o heroinu

1700
01:05:21,340 --> 01:05:24,059
[SPEAKER_00] i kaže, radio je takve gluposti.

1701
01:05:24,059 --> 01:05:26,119
[SPEAKER_00] Mi se možete zamisliti,

1702
01:05:26,119 --> 01:05:27,400
[SPEAKER_00] bio je

1703
01:05:27,400 --> 01:05:29,280
[SPEAKER_00] ovisnik, narkoman.

1704
01:05:29,280 --> 01:05:31,500
[SPEAKER_00] A kaže, svaki put kad bi došao kući,

1705
01:05:31,500 --> 01:05:33,159
[SPEAKER_00] čekao bi ga Tanjur,

1706
01:05:33,159 --> 01:05:34,539
[SPEAKER_00] tople juhe njegove mame.

1707
01:05:34,539 --> 01:05:35,920
[SPEAKER_00] Svakog dana.

1708
01:05:35,920 --> 01:05:37,659
[SPEAKER_00] Svaki put.

1709
01:05:38,719 --> 01:05:40,380
[SPEAKER_00] Dok nije nam došao,

1710
01:05:40,380 --> 01:05:41,840
[SPEAKER_00] vidio taj Tanjur

1711
01:05:41,840 --> 01:05:44,699
[SPEAKER_00] i svatio, čovječe, šta ti radiš?

1712
01:05:44,699 --> 01:05:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] Šta ti radiš sa svojim životom?

1713
01:05:48,000 --> 01:05:53,400
[SPEAKER_00] Topla, ženska, majčinska ljubav

1714
01:05:53,400 --> 01:05:57,059
[SPEAKER_00] je izvukla čovjeka iz takvog zla.

1715
01:05:57,059 --> 01:06:00,679
[SPEAKER_00] Jedan mali iskaz, mali,

1716
01:06:00,679 --> 01:06:03,840
[SPEAKER_00] naše ljubavi i našeg poštovanja.

1717
01:06:08,719 --> 01:06:13,699
[SPEAKER_00] E sad, zadnji neprijatelj,

1718
01:06:13,699 --> 01:06:15,139
[SPEAKER_00] zadnja točka

1719
01:06:15,139 --> 01:06:18,340
[SPEAKER_00] koju ću danas nešto reći je oholost.

1720
01:06:18,340 --> 01:06:20,179
[SPEAKER_00] E sad,

1721
01:06:20,179 --> 01:06:21,940
[SPEAKER_00] korijen naše oholosti je

1722
01:06:21,940 --> 01:06:23,139
[SPEAKER_00] naša nesigurnost

1723
01:06:23,139 --> 01:06:25,059
[SPEAKER_00] i zbog nje možemo stavljati naše zamisli

1724
01:06:25,059 --> 01:06:26,199
[SPEAKER_00] ispred Božji zamisli

1725
01:06:26,199 --> 01:06:29,639
[SPEAKER_00] i naše vrijeme ispred Božjeg vremena.

1726
01:06:31,000 --> 01:06:32,679
[SPEAKER_00] Ja bi se tu opet otaknula

1727
01:06:32,679 --> 01:06:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] odnosa s Bogom.

1728
01:06:34,000 --> 01:06:36,780
[SPEAKER_00] Često kada kukamo

1729
01:06:36,780 --> 01:06:38,099
[SPEAKER_00] i kada više ne znamo šta ćemo

1730
01:06:38,099 --> 01:06:39,539
[SPEAKER_00] pa nas neko pita,

1731
01:06:39,539 --> 01:06:41,199
[SPEAKER_00] više ne znamo šta bi nam rekao,

1732
01:06:41,199 --> 01:06:42,679
[SPEAKER_00] pa je kao kakav ti ono s Bogom,

1733
01:06:42,679 --> 01:06:43,260
[SPEAKER_00] jel moliš?

1734
01:06:43,260 --> 01:06:46,460
[SPEAKER_00] I onda tu dođemo često do tog pitanja,

1735
01:06:46,460 --> 01:06:48,159
[SPEAKER_00] to je isto odgovora,

1736
01:06:48,159 --> 01:06:49,719
[SPEAKER_00] ma ona ne pitaj me, kao.

1737
01:06:49,719 --> 01:06:53,360
[SPEAKER_00] Isrpio sam sva moguća opravdanja

1738
01:06:53,360 --> 01:06:55,739
[SPEAKER_00] da se ne vratim na taj izvor

1739
01:06:55,739 --> 01:06:57,320
[SPEAKER_00] koji mi jedini može donijeti pomoć

1740
01:06:57,320 --> 01:06:59,139
[SPEAKER_00] i više ne znam šta da radim.

1741
01:07:00,460 --> 01:07:03,519
[SPEAKER_00] Ali nema šanse da se vratim tamo

1742
01:07:03,519 --> 01:07:04,159
[SPEAKER_00] gdje mi je mjesto.

1743
01:07:04,159 --> 01:07:07,739
[SPEAKER_00] Ja bi se ovdje u ovom poglavlju

1744
01:07:07,739 --> 01:07:08,820
[SPEAKER_00] posebno dotaknula

1745
01:07:08,820 --> 01:07:11,780
[SPEAKER_00] onih žena, onih ljudi

1746
01:07:11,780 --> 01:07:14,460
[SPEAKER_00] koji su bili dijelom neke zajednice

1747
01:07:14,460 --> 01:07:16,760
[SPEAKER_00] ili na bilo kakav način

1748
01:07:16,760 --> 01:07:19,900
[SPEAKER_00] služili Bogu na takav način.

1749
01:07:19,900 --> 01:07:21,559
[SPEAKER_00] I onda u onom trenutku

1750
01:07:21,559 --> 01:07:24,380
[SPEAKER_00] kada im je Bog ispunio želje

1751
01:07:24,380 --> 01:07:25,900
[SPEAKER_00] da im dobro žene,

1752
01:07:25,900 --> 01:07:28,500
[SPEAKER_00] kada su stvarili

1753
01:07:28,500 --> 01:07:30,840
[SPEAKER_00] u određenim ulogama,

1754
01:07:30,840 --> 01:07:32,159
[SPEAKER_00] više ih nigdje nema.

1755
01:07:32,159 --> 01:07:34,320
[SPEAKER_00] Ajde što nema žena,

1756
01:07:34,320 --> 01:07:35,900
[SPEAKER_00] nego ne daju ni muškarcima.

1757
01:07:35,900 --> 01:07:38,519
[SPEAKER_00] I naravno,

1758
01:07:38,519 --> 01:07:41,460
[SPEAKER_00] da je majčinstvo i vaše dijete

1759
01:07:41,460 --> 01:07:43,099
[SPEAKER_00] na prvom mjestu,

1760
01:07:43,099 --> 01:07:44,380
[SPEAKER_00] vaš obitelj, vaš muži,

1761
01:07:44,380 --> 01:07:45,460
[SPEAKER_00] to niko ne osporava.

1762
01:07:45,460 --> 01:07:47,699
[SPEAKER_00] Vaš obitelj mora biti

1763
01:07:47,699 --> 01:07:48,420
[SPEAKER_00] iznad toga.

1764
01:07:48,420 --> 01:07:50,460
[SPEAKER_00] to je Boži ispravan poredak.

1765
01:07:50,460 --> 01:07:51,980
[SPEAKER_00] Ali,

1766
01:07:51,980 --> 01:07:54,139
[SPEAKER_00] nije ispravno

1767
01:07:54,139 --> 01:07:56,239
[SPEAKER_00] zatvoriti svoje srce za Boga

1768
01:07:56,239 --> 01:07:57,619
[SPEAKER_00] i za njegove potrebe.

1769
01:07:57,619 --> 01:08:00,300
[SPEAKER_00] Ok, ja sad jesam majka

1770
01:08:00,300 --> 01:08:01,719
[SPEAKER_00] i sad ne mogu,

1771
01:08:01,719 --> 01:08:03,079
[SPEAKER_00] možda svaki petak doći

1772
01:08:03,079 --> 01:08:04,059
[SPEAKER_00] na susred zajednice,

1773
01:08:04,059 --> 01:08:06,619
[SPEAKER_00] ali zašto ne bi dozvolilo

1774
01:08:06,619 --> 01:08:07,659
[SPEAKER_00] svome mužu da dođe?

1775
01:08:07,659 --> 01:08:09,820
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto bi nas dvoj sad,

1776
01:08:09,820 --> 01:08:10,880
[SPEAKER_00] troje, morali zajedno

1777
01:08:10,880 --> 01:08:11,840
[SPEAKER_00] ispred doma,

1778
01:08:11,840 --> 01:08:12,739
[SPEAKER_00] petkom gledati

1779
01:08:12,739 --> 01:08:13,860
[SPEAKER_00] susred zajednice

1780
01:08:13,860 --> 01:08:14,579
[SPEAKER_00] ispred ekrana?

1781
01:08:14,579 --> 01:08:15,559
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto?

1782
01:08:15,559 --> 01:08:21,079
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto mi nekad kao obitelj

1783
01:08:21,079 --> 01:08:22,420
[SPEAKER_00] ne bi mogli otići

